      "content": "i get the carbon stuff, but is the \"offset\" actually a proven fact? some studies suggest the ecological damage from mining and the waste from turbine blades at the end of their lives might be more significant than the industry lets on. it seems like a pretty debatable comparison rather than a settled one.",
